$interpreted:
Yan-Bo: Ambition should be made of sterner stuff......
though this be madness, yet there is method in't.
Eh, gotten order wrong yet once more I seem.
Yan-Bo: Stood like statue for days, giving up you are not?
Pang: I will not give up until you make me an apprentice!
Yan-Bo: Of skill I've praised you to have already, why insist?
Pang: Master truly believes in my capabilities?
Yan-Bo: Young one, pray tell. Set your mind you have, hone your martial arts skill you will. But why insist on me?
Pang: Because Master Yan-Bo is much accomplished. I would improve, if given the chance with you.
Yan-Bo: Your intentions are what?
Pang: Be powerful and defeat Tigers' sworn enemies.  Or protect royalty from the threats of assassins.
Yan-Bo: Of Tigers as royal bodyguard, your purpose here Maple Lake is what?
Pang: That, that was in a past I left behind, long ago. I wish to be vigilant against stronger opponents,
Pang: and protect my friends when in need, if I can...
Puggi: Well call me a biscuit! Pang!
Puggi: Hestia's in a fight with the frogodiles, make haste!
Pang: Frogodiles? Are you telling me...?
Hestia: Put that child down, right this instant!
Karnulla: Hmph. It wandered into our territory by itself. Whenever feasible, one should always try to eat the rude. Why should I let it go?
Pang: Both of you...why?
Karnulla: Pang? Have you come to my aid?
Hestia: Pang! Take this bully down with your papi paws!
Hestia: You know Pang?
Karnulla: You do too?
Pang: Everyone, time out. What happened exactly?
Hestia: Hmph. These frogodiles are a threat to Maple Lake, hunting fellow creatures as food without remorse!
Karnulla: Platypuses were destined to be our food. What's wrong with acting on instinct?
Hestia: So tell me, you would kill to save your life? I can't stand you selfish beings any longer!
Karnulla: Everytime we hunt you get in the way. It is I who's lost patience! It's open season, but we're closed off to your voice of reason!
Pang: You both, my friends, please! Let's talk this over!
Karnulla: Pang. Bros over foes, come stand by me!
Hestia: Pang, aren't we supposed to be best friends? Team up with me and take him down!
Pang: This, I...
Hestia: Pang, I'm so disappointed! I've judged you wrong!
Karnulla: I thought we could become blood brothers! Forget it, no use shedding crocodile tears. I'll skin the scales off this fish alive myself!
Karnulla: The old geezer again?!
Yan-Bo: Nature teaches beasts to know their friends. Interfere, I usually would not. Today an exception I make.
Karnulla: UGH. The sight of you makes me lose my appetite. Take this stinking thing back. Bambinos, MOVE!
Yan-Bo: Put an end to the feud you could, strength you have. Remain silent, you have. Allowing the situation to worsen, you did.
Pang: Karnulla and Hestia are both my friends. I-I didn't know what to do, who to help...
Pang: ...Deja vu, I've made the same mistake again...

Yan-Bo: Past has come to haunt you, it has. Causing your mind to be in a mess, it has. 

No matter how you train your physical abilities, first deal with psychological barriers, you must..
Yan-Bo: With me, do you care to walk?
